      "content": "It's incredibly painful when the words offered by others feel hollow and dismissive of the depth of your suffering. Feeling like your pain is permanent and unfixable is a devastating place to be. If the current path feels like endless endurance, perhaps a different kind of support—one that acknowledges the severity of your struggle—could be helpful. Please know that your feelings are valid, and your desire for peace is deeply understood.",
